https://lih.kg/1361703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361703</a><br />\n點解冇人講728中上環遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361287</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">警黑合作，香港政權真面目</span><br />\n西上環事件整合 求更多新聞同義士消息 推上去 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357053</a><br />\n(721)上環+元朗backup片<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354514</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 光復香港 時代革命 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4bba1d51b50b29300cb1ed8a7171af1e94d1f6ef","tid":1369182,"uid":928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"［張建宗是陷阱］凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對［置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369158</a>"},{"pid":"9588edb5fe1cfb9e22bd9715b266d626b191f022","tid":1369182,"uid":928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0e7fffd3c7672655401012b5468b2922fe44d3","tid":1369182,"uid":15719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:26:11.000Z","msg":"其實係好多人太擔心<br />\n因為上星期實在太嬲<br />\n驚前線火遮眼而提下<br />\n並非有心抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9bab9899e1ae3bddd57d278806e7cb2329b0da","tid":1369182,"uid":928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d0e7fffd3c7672655401012b5468b2922fe44d3","tid":1369182,"uid":15719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"r